@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_blezkx(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.exp((v0 - (v2 + 0.04 - v1 + 0.44)))
    tmp = 0.53
    tmp = wp.cos(0.81)
    v2 = v2
    v0 = ((0.76 - wp.sin(tmp + 0.29)) * (wp.abs(v0 + 0.90) - (v1 + 0.99 - tmp + 0.01)))
    data[tid] = v0
